{
  "stem": "3605.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father, in the evening, said, I don't trust those Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I bet you if they are going to run short in number-- because some people ran away, some people hid, and so on-- so they are not going to have the numbers, I bet you they are going to cut off one of the wings that they consider needed or legal, and they are going to send them out.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I am going to hide, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But in the last minute, he gave up the idea of hiding, because he wanted to remain legal to be able to help me, say we both are going to be illegal, we are not going to be able to move at all.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this was the last day of deportation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And sure, he was right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They missed some people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They cut off a wing of those people that were supposed to stay, and they deported them, the last day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my father was between them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they say that all those transports was from my hometown and from Piotrkow went to Treblinka, which was a camp of just destruction.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So that is how I lost my father, in-- at the end of September, 1942.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I remained in that small ghetto, illegal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And prone to all auctions and all-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was also fortunate in the greatest fortune in one thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My father emptied his pockets before he went to the-- to be checked out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he had some valuable things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He had some gold dollars and other things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he put them in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And while he was there, waiting for the deportation, he told it to a Jewish policeman that he emptied his pocket.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And where he emptied it, he should go and tell me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
